Raden Soekemi Sosrodihardjo (a teacher in Surabaya, East Java) is married to Ida Ayu Nyoman Rai (from Buleleng, Bali) and has a child. When they were little their children lived with their grandfathers in Tulungagung, East Java. At the age of 14, their child was invited to live in Surabaya by Oemar Said Tjokroaminoto and sent to school at HBS (Hoogere Burger School). Who is the child in question?
